short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This Plugin will Block Phishing URLs, Domains and IPs

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension will protect users from phishing websites. If a user accidentally clicks on a phishing link, this extension will check whether that domain or URL is phishing. If the link is redirecting the user to a phishing domain or URL, it will automatically block the URL.
